queries.comments: query_name is the name used to reference this query
query_type should always be linked_table for this specific project
linked_form_id is the name of the form to edit for each instance
linked_table_id is the name of the data table that form should effect
selection and selectionArgs are dealing with the database. Selection specifies which fields to be selecting on, and selectionArgs passes in the arguments for the questions marks.
auxillaryHash is used to preload fields in the linked_table. In this case the household_id is made to match the current household_id
creates a roster for the members of the household
filters by both the household_id and the age
